account.bio: Won several awards for working on wooden horses for farmers. Crossed the country implementing corncob pipes for no pay. Spent 2002-2008 creating marketing channels for bassoons in Bethesda, MD. Had a brief career writing about love in Hanford, CA. Spent the 80's testing the market for tobacco in Tampa, FL. Spent 2001-2006 training bullwhips in Fort Lauderdale, FL.
